# This folder is the plugin's translation directory, declared via
# `Domain Path: /languages` in the plugin header. Translators contribute via
# WordPress.org's GlotPress instance once the plugin is published; the .pot
# template is regenerated by the `prepare-release.yml` workflow on every
# version bump and committed alongside the version change.
#
# Local PO/MO files for any language Scene Shift maintains in-house can also
# live here:
#   scene-shift-ai-assistant-en_US.po
#   scene-shift-ai-assistant-en_US.mo
#   scene-shift-ai-assistant.pot
